{"tid":1875453,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[罷韓二階完成] 罷韓連署今晚破23萬份，已達法定門檻","createTime":"2020-02-11T19:58:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-20T03:02:34.000Z","uid":52658,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a0254ea4c4daeb0e1581c5f76342ab4c4017c2cd","tid":1875453,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T19:58:59.000Z","msg":"罷免高雄市長韓國瑜的第二階段連署，今晚（11日）最新統計已達23萬0753份，超過法定門檻約22.8萬份！將繼續朝30萬份邁進。<br />\n<br />\n不懼武漢肺炎攪局，罷韓二階連署從1月29日展開，在高雄市各地反應熱烈，公民團體統計到今天（11日）深夜，僅14天就收到23萬0753份，跨越法定門檻約22.8萬份。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n光復高雄 <br />\n時代力量"},{"pid":"b22b681ad070e6bd85334c56f87612eb8a8b08e1","tid":1875453,"uid":254183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T20:03:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f25bb7bad761e9ffa2f0937c188c2694a7db5ece","tid":1875453,"uid":52658,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T20:06:48.000Z","msg":"其實都幾誇張<br />\n高雄200萬人口<br />\n14日已經有10分1人出黎聯署要罷免佢<br />\n證明條友都幾乞鳩人憎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dc6fe10de54490b5e4d2b20535fdb166f0102f0","tid":1875453,"uid":252069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T20:21:46.000Z","msg":"香城教育電視: 請你哋將一部份口罩經由黃店派出<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1875445\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1875445</a>"},{"pid":"6ca01bdc34f89075c89eb4a8122ba2e08b1af8c5","tid":1875453